{"tid":2086931,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"七一港殤書","createTime":"2020-06-30T13:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T16:36:03.000Z","uid":6842,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3337c4346bc746e9e2390d834744c3dae42df47","tid":2086931,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:24:24.000Z","msg":"今晚夜 遞來恐嚇信<br />\n來自一位虎視廿年 港區的中共<br />\n難道只可給你詐言惑眾<br />\n只想加速滅亡才要硬上弓<br />\n<br />\n如國安即將通過 不甘的我 餘生都枉過麼<br />\n若我走出了大隊 失去什麼 你可想過<br />\n很想我以後能愛國 獎我肺白如花麼<br />\n天真低首想法太多<br />\n誰有心演一齣戲 靜思己過 林太蛻變月娥<br />\n茫然撐立法 為偉大領導寶座<br />\n若送中給錯過 用國安的法例拉我"},{"pid":"6f7b91fc3a44526f1b34ef544cb5c64687b10299","tid":2086931,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx0vodRn.png&amp;h=bffec503&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z74Hva5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ74Hva5.png&h=a1d38e47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd3b89a1ba35171fd127b88dc782cef0dff64e66","tid":2086931,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e59b2ab823330609dbe0fab4e0006b6d761a563","tid":2086931,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17aaeb7a49244b895a40dda471762fe3880d89e4","tid":2086931,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" clas